@startuml
|Maintenance|
start
:Authenticate as technician;
:Enter maintenance mode;
:Inspect cash cassettes and paper;
if (Refill required?) then (yes)
  :Refill cash and paper;
endif
:Run diagnostics;
if (Faults found?) then (yes)
  :Log issues and repair as needed;
endif
:Exit maintenance mode;
stop
@enduml
